company.name: Ultimate Institute of Australia (UIA)
company.description:
Ultimate Institute of Australia (UIA) combines a proud legacy of delivering quality education and a new, reinvigorated commitment to its students. Founded in 2016 as Rachi Systems t/a Logitrain, UIA re-established itself in 2016, under a new management as a revitalized Registered Training Organisation (RTO), combining a decade-long legacy and a bolstered vision and commitment. Our commitment is to deliver quality, practical training to produce industry-savvy graduates ready to enter and succeed in the workforce.
A young, dynamic institute, UIA offers courses ranging from Certificate IV to Advanced Diploma in Business and Graduate Diploma, Information Technology (IT) to international students. Our mission is to empower students with the knowledge and skills in Business and Information Technology that will prepare them for the competitive job market and empower them to achieve a long and successful career in their chosen industry.

● We are committed to empowering students with the knowledge and skills to succeed, and continue lifelong learning in their chosen field. We achieve this through programs contextualized for current and future industry needs and standards.

● We offer students the opportunity to study relevant, practical programs in state-of-the-art facilities in the heart of Melbourne’s Central Business District (CBD).

● We encourage students interested in succeeding and prepared for lifelong learning join in our success, and make a valuable contribution Australian education.
